						<div class="postbody">Which mirroiting mode shall I choose to have a single bi-directionnal scrolling screen ? What are the strong points and the weak points of Horizontal / Vertical mirroiting ?</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Life is complex: it has both real and imaginary components.</div>
